Package com.panizales.curriculum

Class Curriculum

java.lang.Object
com.panizales.Item
com.panizales.curriculum.Curriculum
All Implemented Interfaces:
DisplayInterface, java.lang.Cloneable
public class Curriculum
extends Item
implements java.lang.Cloneable
Curriculum represents a curriculum object. A curriculum has the following properties: (1) startingYear (2) endingYear (3) semester (under which it is implemented) (4) studentYearLevel (the year level of students taking that curriculum) (5) courseList -- list of courses particular to a specific curriculum This class provides methods for dealing with a curriculum object on an individual level
Author:
PatrickPanizales
